{"tid":689544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"介紹返, 新上架交友app, Flip","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:52:52.000Z","uid":63213,"like":4,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"455843a1c0ed4031f82197c6bdc7733155fd32ab","tid":689544,"uid":63213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的. 我同個朋友一齊開發緊個交友app. 上架無耐, 基本上仲係發展緊, 人唔多. 慢慢會有更新. 想大家俾啲意見.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目前只有iOS 版: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/flip-real-connections/id1334147533?l=en&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fflip-real-connections%2Fid1334147533%3Fl%3Den%26mt%3D8&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=baeee220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/flip-real-connections/id1334147533?l=en&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n以前玩過嘅app. 有時覺得複雜咗d, 所以設計上盡量簡約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家基本成型, 主打幾樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n- 認證. 所有會員要經認證, post一張個人相, 再即開相機影張selfie. 經我地認證完先用到.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 地圖. 左掃右掃已經好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> . 雖然app上面仲有呢種形式, 但係地圖係我地重點發展.<br />\n- 當有人like咗你, 就會出現notification. 當然我地唔會明示你, 等你自己感應下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多功能想加同改進. 而家條team得幾丁友, 一路路改. 希望聽下其他人想要d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5ab43dce51f8aa601aacf6763526de05a9bc56","tid":689544,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:11:43.000Z","msg":"網上馬伕"},{"pid":"83defd04338c2505772a1a2683cb4b9806e75de5","tid":689544,"uid":88335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"偷食app?"},{"pid":"3536ecd0da459a479a69ee0752633fe437481d77","tid":689544,"uid":20241,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:16:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呢啲app害撚死幾多人 搞死幾多家庭情侶<br />\n真心希望搞呢啲交友app既人死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57efb436982c3975649acfb91db3ea0751520ec5","tid":689544,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"Fap?"},{"pid":"672ae54c32a001e6d9ad4af2dc7b2a033bba2b69","tid":689544,"uid":63213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"我都明白app 上有唔同類型人。app本身只係工具。我地出發點亦係一個正經交友app, 所以我地加入認證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地唔係為厹服務，我都想聽下係你角度，加入咩功能可以幫助防止歪風出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e636ecc7c2ae604a6b9eac81e1cd43a7d5bc7c1","tid":689544,"uid":5676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"用緊，好少人，like左三十個都唔知有冇"},{"pid":"841f835676ccef1fca06de5ea6198366c9a068b6","tid":689544,"uid":63213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e636ecc7c2ae604a6b9eac81e1cd43a7d5bc7c1","tid":689544,"uid":5676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:32:02.000Z","msg":"用緊，好少人，like左三十個都唔知有冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為開咗無耐，但又未至於得30個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你會唔會filter咗一堆？"},{"pid":"bf3fb3d5982c707dc14b020e1c4e300bc9fc15ac","tid":689544,"uid":31515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"人手驗證定machine learning？"},{"pid":"14834d1bf275c62075d1dfe89df2e485eeceda6e","tid":689544,"uid":65333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"買評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473222588f353c2108b1846272858238